{"tid":797262,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"小丸子死咗","createTime":"2018-08-28T11:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T12:07:08.000Z","uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0654d3a71b40fe7ae059014a740d88f5ef27099a","tid":797262,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好感慨  一直覺得同小丸子關係親蜜 心有點痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ad97da1c9504e36255b32249a0b05afd85aaff","tid":797262,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:35:12.000Z","msg":"日本長青漫畫《櫻桃小丸子》的原作者櫻桃子，今日傳出死訊，其網誌公布其離世消息，櫻桃子於2018年8月15日晚上8時29分，因乳癌與世長辭，終年53歲。在櫻桃子家人的意願下，喪禮已在日前舉行。 <br />\n<br />\n櫻桃子老師於1984年以漫畫家的身份出道，引用櫻桃子老師於出道30週年時的一句話：「在這30年間，不論是美好的事或艱辛的事都有很多，但大家都讓我作為作家過了非常幸福的月日。光是感謝仍不足以形容我的心情。」‐摘錄自《『櫻桃子的世界展』「迎來出道30週年」》。她對於能夠繪畫出一部讓大家能樂在其中的作品，表示非常感恩"},{"pid":"c34268fd119fb6df833b9450b8a0696d51a2fcc8","tid":797262,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:46:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06590e072317b6266d00c3db2c8aa8edb915610e","tid":797262,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c34268fd119fb6df833b9450b8a0696d51a2fcc8","tid":797262,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:46:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:46:28.000Z","msg":"翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoj